tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_reports (
  website_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  traffic_date DATE,
  page_views INT,
  unique_visitors INT,
  conversion_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
  page_conversion VARCHAR(255),
  source_page VARCHAR(255),
  destination_page VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   page_url TEXT,
   visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   visitor_id INT,
   referral_source TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   page_url TEXT,
   conversion_event TIMESTAMP,
   visitor_id INT,
   conversion_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE performance_analysis (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   page_url TEXT,
   visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   visitor_id INT,
   conversion_event TIMESTAMP,
   conversion_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE WebsiteVisits (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visit_date DATE,
  visitor_ip VARCHAR(50),
  page_visited VARCHAR(100),
  conversion_status BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE PageViews (
  page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  page_title VARCHAR(100),
  average_time_spent INT,
  unique_visitors_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE ConversionRates (
  conversion_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  conversion_date DATE,
  page_id INT,
  visitor_ip VARCHAR(50),
  conversion_status BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE TrafficSources (
  source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name VARCHAR(50),
  source_type VARCHAR(50),
  daily_visits_count INT,
  conversion_rate FLOAT
)
